<i>They were Hlinka Guards,</i>

33
00:02:59.991 --> 00:03:02.694
<i>Slovakian State Police.</i>

34
00:03:03.494 --> 00:03:06.898
Make sure to get
all the alleyways this time,


35
00:03:07.031 --> 00:03:09.266
not just the main square.

36
00:03:10.034 --> 00:03:11.536
The whole Jewish quarter?

37
00:03:12.102 --> 00:03:13.370
Yes.

38
00:03:16.040 --> 00:03:18.408
Every Jew, that's what it says.

39
00:03:18.543 --> 00:03:20.678
So everyone
can see it and read it.


40
00:03:20.812 --> 00:03:24.281
[Emil] <i>They had to make sure</i>
<i>that every Jew in Bardejov</i>


41
00:03:24.415 --> 00:03:26.517
<i>knew what was expected of them.</i>

42
00:03:26.651 --> 00:03:28.553
[Mrs. Schondof]
Thomas, is that you?


43
00:03:29.219 --> 00:03:30.822
Good morning, Mrs. Schondof.

44
00:03:30.955 --> 00:03:32.490
-Hi, Thomas.
-Hi.


45
00:03:32.624 --> 00:03:34.224
[Emil] <i>It was mostly</i>
<i>friends and neighbors</i>


46
00:03:34.358 --> 00:03:35.325
<i>who brought them the news.</i>

47
00:03:35.460 --> 00:03:36.561
Why so early?

48
00:03:36.694 --> 00:03:38.663
Oh, I'm so sorry for waking you.

49
00:03:38.796 --> 00:03:40.031
